lines: 3m dyneon fluoroplastic granules thv 221gz is a fluorothermoplastic containing tetrafluoroethylene, hexafluoropropylene and vinylidene fluoride.
processing profile allows co-processing with olefinic plastics and hydrocarbon elastomers
thv 221gz is a flexible, transparent fluoroplastic composed of tetrafluoroethylene, hexafluoropropylene, and vinylidene fluoride in the form of pellets
provides a balance of low temperature processing, low flammability, thermal stability, and melt processability.
